 21-year-old brother. The shooter said he did not had a good relation with the two girls, and said that they ridiculed him publicly.<ref>[https://noticias.uol.com.br/inter/reuters/2002/10/28/ult27u27985.jhtm Estudante mata duas colegas dentro de escola em Salvador], ''UOL Not\u00edcias'' (October 28, 2002)</ref><ref>[http://www1.folha.uol.com.br/fsp/cotidian/ff2910200203.htm Na BA, estudante mata 2 colegas na sala de aula], ''[[Folha de S.Paulo]]'' (October 29, 2002)</ref><ref>[http://www.correio24horas.com.br/noticia/nid/relembre-caso-de-adolescente-que-matou-colegas-em-escola-em-salvador/ Relembre caso de adolescente que matou colegas em escola em Salvador], ''Correio'' (April 7, 2011)</ref>\n|-\n| January 26, 2003\n| [[Guangdong|Suixi county]], [[China]]\n| Chen Peiquan, 35\n| 4 dead\n| 3 injured\n| Chen Peiquan, an English teacher with a history of mental problems, stabbed six students and a teacher in a dormitory at Yang Gan Middle School, killing four of them. He was arrested after fleeing to the roof of the building.<ref>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/en/doc/2003-01/28/content_153227.htm Teacher stabs seven in China, three children and a teacher die], ''[[China Daily]]'' (January 28, 2006)</ref><ref>[http://www.news24.com/News24/World/0,6119,2-10_1312135,00.html Teacher goes berserk, kills 4]{{dead link|date=May 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}, ''[[News24]]'' (January 27, 2003)</ref>\n|-\n| January 27, 2003\n| [[Taiuva]], [[Brazil]]\n| Edmar Aparecido Freitas, 18\n| 1 dead\n| 8 injured\n| 18-year-old Edmar Freitas shot and wounded six students, a teacher and a janitor with a 38-caliber revolver at Escola Estadual Coronel Benedito Ortiz, his former school where he had been bullied for being overweight. He then committed suicide by shooting himself in the head.<ref>[http://www2.correioweb.com.br/cw/EDICAO_20030128/pri_ult_280103_215.htm Jovem invade escola, fere oito e se suicida], ''[[Correio Braziliense]]'' (January 28, 2003)</ref><ref>[http