okela school shooting]]. 18-year-old student Pekka-Eric Auvinen opened fire with a [[.22 Long Rifle|.22-caliber]] [[semi-automatic handgun|semi-automatic]] [[SIG Mosquito|SIG Mosquito pistol]] at [[Jokela High School]], in [[Tuusula]], Finland. Six students, the school principal, and the school nurse were killed. The forty-minute attack ended when Auvinen shot himself in the head, later dying that evening at a [[Helsinki]] hospital.\n|-\n| December 11, 2007\n| [[Gurgaon]],<br>[[Haryana]],<br>India\n| Akash Vadav, 14;<br>Vikas Yadav, 13\n| 1 dead\n|\n| 14-year-old student Abhishek Tyagi was shot five times at the Euro International School, in [[Gurgaon]], India. Two other students, 14-year-old Akash Vadav and 13-year-old Vikas Yadav, were charged in connection with the shooting.<ref name=\"hindustani1212\">{{cite news|title=School students shoot classmate for \u2018bullying\u2019|date=2007-12-12|url =http://hindustantimes.com/StoryPage/StoryPage.aspx?id=df416321-98a6-4572-b0bf-c6c5fbf29902&MatchID1=4604&TeamID1=6&TeamID2=7&MatchType1=1&SeriesID1=1157&MatchID2=4575&TeamID3=8&TeamID4=2&MatchType2=1&SeriesID2=1147&PrimaryID=4604&Headline=School+students+shoot+classmate+for+%e2%80%98bullying%e2%80%99|work=[[Hindustan Times]]|accessdate = 2009-04-25}}</ref>\n|-\n| December 21, 2007\n| [[Union City, California|Union City]],<br>[[California]],<br>United States\n| Unknown\n| 1 dead\n|\n| Vernon Matthew Eddins, a 14-year-old student of [[James Logan High School]], was shot dead at the doorstep of Barnard-White Middle School, in [[Union City, California]].<ref name=\"usatodayviolencemap\">{{cite news|title=Mapping school violence|date=2009-04-12|agency= [[Associated Press]]|url =https://www.usatoday.com/news/nation/graphic-school-killings.htm|work=[[USA Today]]|accessdate = 2009-05-03}}</ref><ref name=\"baycitychronicle1221\">{{cite news|title=Boy shot dead in front of middle school |date=2007-12-21 |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=/baycitynews/archive/2007/